{"id":17635,"date":"2019-02-07T16:39:08","date_gmt":"2019-02-07T11:09:08","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/?p=17635"},"modified":"2023-05-18T10:51:33","modified_gmt":"2023-05-18T05:21:33","slug":"robert-vadra","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/robert-vadra\/","title":{"rendered":"Robert Vadra Wiki, Age, Wife, Controversy, Family, Biography &amp; More"},"content":{"rendered":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/Robert-Vadra.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-17636\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/Robert-Vadra.jpg\" alt=\"Robert Vadra\" width=\"533\" height=\"404\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/Robert-Vadra.jpg 660w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/Robert-Vadra-300x227.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 533px) 100vw, 533px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p><strong>Robert Rajendra Vadra<\/strong> is an Indian Businessman and related to the renowned Nehru-Gandhi family. He is the son-in-law of the former Indian Prime Minister, Rajiv Gandhi and brother-in-law of the Congress President, <a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/rahul-gandhi\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Rahul Gandhi<\/a>.<\/p>\n<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_62 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-custom ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">Contents<\/p>\n<label for=\"ez-toc-cssicon-toggle-item-65bce3bc077d1\" class=\"ez-toc-cssicon-toggle-label\"><span class=\"\"><span class=\"eztoc-hide\" style=\"display:none;\">Toggle<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-icon-toggle-span\"><svg style=\"fill: #000000;color:#000000\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"list-377408\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z\" fill=\"currentColor\"><\/path><\/svg><svg style=\"fill: #000000;color:#000000\" class=\"arrow-unsorted-368013\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" version=\"1.2\" baseProfile=\"tiny\"><path d=\"M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z\"\/><\/svg><\/span><\/span><\/label><input type=\"checkbox\"  id=\"ez-toc-cssicon-toggle-item-65bce3bc077d1\"  aria-label=\"Toggle\" \/><nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 ' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/robert-vadra\/#Physical_Appearance\" title=\"Physical Appearance\">Physical Appearance<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/robert-vadra\/#WikiBiography\" title=\"Wiki\/Biography\">Wiki\/Biography<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/robert-vadra\/#Family_Caste_Wife\" title=\"Family, Caste &amp; Wife\">Family, Caste &amp; Wife<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/robert-vadra\/#Career\" title=\"Career\">Career<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/robert-vadra\/#Controversies\" title=\"Controversies\">Controversies<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/robert-vadra\/#Style_Quotient\" title=\"Style\u00a0Quotient\">Style\u00a0Quotient<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/robert-vadra\/#AssetsNet_Worth\" title=\"Assets\/Net Worth\">Assets\/Net Worth<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/robert-vadra\/#Facts\" title=\"Facts\">Facts<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Physical_Appearance\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #800080;\">Physical Appearance<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>He is about 5 feet 5 inch or 167 cm tall and weighs in about 70 kg or 154 lbs. His eye and hair colour is black.<a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/Robert-Vadra-working-out.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-17655\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/Robert-Vadra-working-out.jpg\" alt=\"Robert Vadra working out\" width=\"400\" height=\"537\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/Robert-Vadra-working-out.jpg 400w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/Robert-Vadra-working-out-223x300.jpg 223w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"WikiBiography\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #800080;\">Wiki\/Biography<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Robert Vadra was born in a Christian family on\u00a018 May 1969 (<strong>Age: 54 years, as of 2023<\/strong>) in\u00a0Moradabad,\u00a0Uttar Pradesh, India. His family originally belongs to Sialkot, Punjab, Pakistan. His father migrated to India during the partition of India. His father, Rajendra Vadra\u00a0ran a brass and wood handicrafts business in Moradabad. His mother,\u00a0 Maureen had Scottish descent. Robert did his schooling from the British School, New Delhi.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Family_Caste_Wife\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #800080;\">Family, Caste &amp; Wife<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Robert Vadra was born to Rajendra Vadra and Maureen Vadra. His father is a <strong>Punjabi Khatri<\/strong> while his mother is a <strong>Christian<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_17637\" style=\"width: 438px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/Robert-Vadra-with-his-mother.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-17637\" class=\" wp-image-17637\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/Robert-Vadra-with-his-mother.jpg\" alt=\"Robert Vadra with his mother\" width=\"428\" height=\"428\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/Robert-Vadra-with-his-mother.jpg 500w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/Robert-Vadra-with-his-mother-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/Robert-Vadra-with-his-mother-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/Robert-Vadra-with-his-mother-65x65.jpg 65w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 428px) 100vw, 428px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-17637\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Robert Vadra with his mother<\/p><\/div>\n<p>He has two siblings; one brother-\u00a0Richard Vadra and one sister-\u00a0Michelle Vadra. However, his both siblings have passed away.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_17638\" style=\"width: 316px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/Richard-Vadra-brother-of-Robert-Vadra.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-17638\" class=\" wp-image-17638\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/Richard-Vadra-brother-of-Robert-Vadra.jpg\" alt=\"Richard Vadra, brother of Robert Vadra\" width=\"306\" height=\"366\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/Richard-Vadra-brother-of-Robert-Vadra.jpg 400w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/Richard-Vadra-brother-of-Robert-Vadra-251x300.jpg 251w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 306px) 100vw, 306px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-17638\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Richard Vadra, brother of Robert Vadra<\/p><\/div>\n<p>He married <a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/priyanka-gandhi\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Priyanka Gandhi<\/a>, the daughter of former Prime Minister of India, <a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/rajiv-gandhi\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Rajiv Gandhi<\/a> and former Congress President, <a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/sonia-gandhi\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Sonia Gandhi<\/a> on 18 February 1997. To get married to Priyanka, Robert had to <strong>convert to Hinduism<\/strong>. <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_17635_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_17635_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_17635_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_17635_1_1\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[1]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_17635_1_1\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"http:\/\/www.rediff.com\/news\/feb\/10gandhi.htm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Rediff<\/a><\/span><\/span> Robert and Priyanka were classmates and met at a friend&#8217;s home for the first time. They fell in love with each other and got married. Initially, both families were not ready for the marriage, but due to the stubbornness of Priyanka Gandhi, they had to agree.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_16659\" style=\"width: 576px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/Priyanka-Gandhi-with-her-husband-at-the-time-of-wedding.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-16659\" class=\" wp-image-16659\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/Priyanka-Gandhi-with-her-husband-at-the-time-of-wedding.jpg\" alt=\"Robert Vadra and Priyanka Gandhi at the time of their wedding\" width=\"566\" height=\"415\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/Priyanka-Gandhi-with-her-husband-at-the-time-of-wedding.jpg 640w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/Priyanka-Gandhi-with-her-husband-at-the-time-of-wedding-300x220.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 566px) 100vw, 566px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-16659\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Robert Vadra and Priyanka Gandhi at the time of their wedding<\/p><\/div>\n<p>The couple has two children: a son, Rehan (born in 2000) and a daughter, Miraya (born in 2002).<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_17639\" style=\"width: 288px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/Robert-Vadra-with-his-son-and-daughter.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-17639\" class=\"size-full wp-image-17639\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/Robert-Vadra-with-his-son-and-daughter.jpg\" alt=\"Robert Vadra with his son and daughter\" width=\"278\" height=\"381\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/Robert-Vadra-with-his-son-and-daughter.jpg 278w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/Robert-Vadra-with-his-son-and-daughter-219x300.jpg 219w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 278px) 100vw, 278px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-17639\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Robert Vadra with his son and daughter<\/p><\/div>\n<p>Congress President, <a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/rahul-gandhi\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Rahul Gandhi<\/a> is his brother-in-law.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_17640\" style=\"width: 497px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/Robert-Vadra-with-Rahul-Gandhi.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-17640\" class=\" wp-image-17640\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/Robert-Vadra-with-Rahul-Gandhi.jpg\" alt=\"Robert Vadra with Rahul Gandhi\" width=\"487\" height=\"274\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/Robert-Vadra-with-Rahul-Gandhi.jpg 640w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/Robert-Vadra-with-Rahul-Gandhi-300x169.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 487px) 100vw, 487px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-17640\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Robert Vadra with Rahul Gandhi<\/p><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Career\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #800080;\">Career<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>He is a businessman, however, his business career has been controversial in the media. He along with his mother is the director of\u00a0Sky Light Hospitality Private Limited which is a conglomerate company and deals in bars, restaurants, canteens, etc.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Controversies\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #800080;\">Controversies<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>He has been accused of misusing his ties with Gandhi-family\u00a0to seek favours inside and outside of Congress party.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>During the Anti-Corruption movement in 2012, then activist Arvind Kejriwal accused him of illegal deals between real-estate giant DLF and Vadra. He targeted DLF that it had gifted\u00a0Vadra an interest-free loan of Rs. 65 crore as well as discounted apartments in Gurgaon.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>On 1 September 2018, an FIR was lodged against\u00a0Robert Vadra and Bhupinder Singh Hooda (former Haryana Chief Minister) at Kherki Daula Police Station in Gurgaon over alleged irregularities in land deals in Gurgaon.\n<p><div id=\"attachment_17653\" style=\"width: 412px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/FIR-against-Robert-Vadra.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-17653\" class=\"size-full wp-image-17653\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/FIR-against-Robert-Vadra.jpg\" alt=\"FIR against Robert Vadra\" width=\"402\" height=\"372\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/FIR-against-Robert-Vadra.jpg 402w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/FIR-against-Robert-Vadra-300x278.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 402px) 100vw, 402px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-17653\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">FIR against Robert Vadra<\/p><\/div><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Vadra has also been accused of having\u00a0Connections with controversial arms dealer Sanjay Bhandari. <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_17635_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_17635_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_17635_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_17635_1_2\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[2]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_17635_1_2\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/www.indiatvnews.com\/politics\/national-5-controversies-surrounding-trobert-vadra-332235\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\">IndiaTV<\/a><\/span><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>In 2010, several allegations were made on Robert Vandra by several Indian politicians that he was connected\u00a0to the CWG (Commonwealth Games) scam of around \u20b910,000 Crores; which were hosted by India.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Style_Quotient\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #800080;\">Style\u00a0Quotient<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>He owns several cars;\u00a0Mercedes, BMW, Land Rover, Jaguar,\u00a0Porsche Panamera, etc.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_17671\" style=\"width: 610px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/Robert-Vadra-in-his-Porshe.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-17671\" class=\"size-full wp-image-17671\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/Robert-Vadra-in-his-Porshe.jpg\" alt=\"Robert Vadra in his Porshe\" width=\"600\" height=\"402\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/Robert-Vadra-in-his-Porshe.jpg 600w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/Robert-Vadra-in-his-Porshe-300x200.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-17671\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Robert Vadra in his Porshe<\/p><\/div>\n<p>He owns several bikes also such as\u00a0Suzuki Intruder, Suzuki Boulevard, etc.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_17670\" style=\"width: 483px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/Robert-Vadra-on-his-bike.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-17670\" class=\" wp-image-17670\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/Robert-Vadra-on-his-bike.jpg\" alt=\"Robert Vadra on his bike\" width=\"473\" height=\"315\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/Robert-Vadra-on-his-bike.jpg 650w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/Robert-Vadra-on-his-bike-300x200.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 473px) 100vw, 473px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-17670\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Robert Vadra on his bike<\/p><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"AssetsNet_Worth\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #800080;\">Assets\/Net Worth<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>He has a total net worth of $2.1 billion.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Facts\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #800080;\">Facts<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Vadra dropped out of college and joined his family business of brassware and artificial jewellery.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>In 1985, he first met Priyanka Gandhi through his sister\u00a0Michelle Vadra; at that time Priyanka was just 13 years old. He supported Priyanka in her tough time after the\u00a0assassination of her father, Rajiv Gandhi.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>In 1997, he started Artex (a handicraft business). Later, he got into other businesses including hospitality and real estate. His mother Maureen Vadra is the Director of all his companies.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>In 2001, he lost his sister, Michelle, in a car accident. In 2003, his brother, Richard Vadra committed suicide and in 2009, his father\u2019s dead body was found at a Delhi motel.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Between November 2007 and June 2008, he opened a number of companies; Sky Light Hospitality, Sky Light Realty, Real Earth Estates, North India IT Parks, Blue Breeze Trading, and others. All these businesses began with a paid-up capital between\u00a0\u20b95 Lakh to\u00a0\u20b925 Lakh.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Vadra is the owner of many\u00a0Hilton Hotels\u00a0including Hilton Gardens, New Delhi. He also has stakes in DLF (Real Estate Company) and DLF IPL (Indian Premier League).<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>In 2014, he was highly trolled for his statement \u201cAre you serious?\u201d reaction to the media reporter on asking questions regarding the land deal.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><iframe title=\"Robert Vadra pushes mic away, asks &quot;Are you serious&quot;?\" width=\"1060\" height=\"795\" src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/PI2V40M_rHg?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen><\/iframe><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>He is a fitness freak. He has a passion for an exhausting workout in the gym.\n<p><div id=\"attachment_17669\" style=\"width: 650px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/Robert-Vadra-working-out-in-gym.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-17669\" class=\"size-full wp-image-17669\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/Robert-Vadra-working-out-in-gym.jpg\" alt=\"Robert Vadra working out in gym\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/Robert-Vadra-working-out-in-gym.jpg 640w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/Robert-Vadra-working-out-in-gym-300x169.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-17669\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Robert Vadra working out in a gym<\/p><\/div><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div class=\"489bcfb86580b123547338c91db0eff2\" data-index=\"3\" style=\"float: none; margin:3px 0 3px 0; text-align:center;\">\n<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\"\r\n     style=\"display:block\"\r\n     data-ad-format=\"autorelaxed\"\r\n     data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6769524711517462\"\r\n     data-ad-slot=\"2473600074\"><\/ins>\n<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"font-size: 0px; height: 0px; line-height: 0px; margin: 0; padding: 0; clear: both;\"><\/div><div class=\"speaker-mute footnotes_reference_container\"> <div class=\"footnote_container_prepare\"><p><span role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" id=\"footnotes_container_label_expand_17635_1\" class=\"footnote_reference_container_label pointer\" on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_17635_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed),footnotes_container_button_plus_17635_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed),footnotes_container_button_minus_17635_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed)\">References<\/span><span role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" id=\"footnotes_container_button_plus_17635_1\" class=\"footnote_reference_container_collapse_button\" on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_17635_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed),footnotes_container_button_plus_17635_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed),footnotes_container_button_minus_17635_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed)\">[+]<\/span><span><\/span><span role=\"button\" tabind